summary:
Whiterun Now Has A Battle Arena For All Your Battling Needs!
Arena Entry Is Under The Small Bridge When You First Enter Whiterun
There Is A Group Of Monsters Waiting In The Combat Ring To Fight And When You Kill Them You Can Always Spawn More To Fight With Console Commands.

Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mTwjQ
